 along with a desirable lower surface\ndistance. Ultimately, our model provides a robust way of accurately reducing\nsegmentation errors in complex multi-tissue interfacing areas of brain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2022 18:21:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2022 18:07:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2023 02:55:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-09"}
