\nto both worst-case optimality in terms of expected regret order and\nlight-tailed risk on the regret distribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 02:10:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jun 2022 02:16:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 16:15:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2022 18:43:11 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 02:43:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
