 devised. Extensive simulations are conducted to verify the\neffectiveness of the proposed FL-EOCD algorithm over FL conventional schemes in\nterms of energy consumption, latency, and convergence rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 02:54:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
