y provide strong arguments in favor of the interchange reconnection origin\nof switchbacks. Metis measurements suggest that the initiation of the\nswitchback may also be an indicator of the origin of slow solar wind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 08:13:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 10:57:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
