itized solar cells\nsince the critical temperature for the onset of self-metalation is very close\nto the normal operating temperature of photovoltaic devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 10:55:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2022 08:37:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-09"}
